data.description: Incredibly appealing mid-century on live oak canopied street in one of SW Houstons best kept secrets...Post Oak Manor. Where do you get this upbeat vibe in the $200s? From the slated front porch and large Living Room window by Pella to decorative sconces and pristine landscape to the fresh paint scheme.... it feels like HOME. The same feel extends to interior with hardwood floors, shiplap accent wall, upgraded granite kitchen with all SS appliances; oversized master retreat with large bath and walk-in closet. Generous secondary bedrooms in a split plan also feature large closets. French doors to brick paver patio, shady backyard and room for pool. Aggressively priced for mortgage payments comparable to smaller apartments. Refrigerator, Washer and dryer to remain. No history of flooding!
